The approach chosen for the calculation of site energies, that is, the diagonal elements of the excitonic Hamiltonian of the aggregate (Eq. (2)), is similar to the approach used for charge transport in our previously developed FOB-SH17,18. The potential energy of the excitonic state ϕkXT\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
