				\begin{document}$${\chi }_{k}^{{{{{{{{\rm{L}}}}}}}}}$$\end{document}, k the site index, k = 1, 2. In the initial state (1) the electron on site 1 is in the excited state and the electron on site 2 is in the ground state and vice versa for the final state (2). The corresponding wavefunctions are ϕ1XT=2−1/2det(χ1L(r1)χ2H(r2))\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
